2002-10-07  Brian T. N. Gunney  <gunneyb@llnl.gov>

	* acmacros: Macros that generate files at configure
	time should add those files to the DISTCLEANFILES
	variables to be cleaned up at distclean time.

2001-09-27  Brian T. N. Gunney  <gunneyb@llnl.gov>

	* configure.in, Makefile.am: Added configuration
	files to test macros.

2001-06-20  Brian T. N. Gunney  <gunneyb@llnl.gov>

	* arg-with-environment.m4, variable-header-filenames.m4:
	Make default tasks for optionl arguments.

2001-05-04  Brian T. N. Gunney  <gunneyb@llnl.gov>

	* compiling-stl.m4: No longer contains macros
	for finding correct header filenames.  Those
	were move to variable-header-filenames.m4.

	* variable-header-filenames.m4: File replaces
	compiling-stl.m4, which was more general than
	for stl alone.

2001-03-27  Brian T. N. Gunney  <gunneyb@llnl.gov>

	* configure-log.m4: Allows logging of multiple
	variables in one call.

2001-03-20  Brian T. N. Gunney  <gunneyb@llnl.gov>

	* choose-mp-interface.m4 (enable_mp_interface): Added
	file with macros for setting C macro indicating
	message passing interface to support.

2001-03-14  Brian T. N. Gunney  <gunneyb@llnl.gov>

	* configure-log.m4: Added specialization for logging
	variables.

	* compiling-stl.m4: Add macros to check names of
	iostream, iomanip and fstream classes.

	* compiling-namespace.m4: Improved namespace test code.

	* specify-ar.m4: Use compiler id instead of compiler name.

2001-03-05  Brian T. N. Gunney  <gunney@llnl.gov>

	* with-prefix.m4: Generalized so that the variable
	set is not fixed.

2001-03-02  Brian T. N. Gunney  <gunney@llnl.gov>

	* with-prefix.m4: New file.  Define macro to specify
	where a software package is installed (its prefix).

2001-02-22  Brian T. N. Gunney  <gunney@cogneato.llnl.gov>

	* compiler-id.m4: Pre-eval eval added for IBM because
	it does not eval correctly in one step.

2001-02-20  Brian T. N. Gunney  <gunney@cogneato.llnl.gov>

	* support-lam.m4: Added file support-lam.m4.

2001-02-14  Brian T. N. Gunney  <gunney@cogneato.llnl.gov>

	* choose-STL.m4: Added prefix BTNG_ to names to avoid clash
	with PADRE version.

	* compiler-id.m4: Added entries for SGI and IBM.

